NK007(ja)001:5113: dpal ldan rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK007(ja)001:5114: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK007(ja)001:5115: deng bdag 'jam dpal sku gsung thugs 'dzin pas //
NK007(ja)001:5116: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK007(ja)001:5117: k+aa ya sid+d+hi h'u +aah w+aak+ka sid+d+hi h'u +aahtsit+ta sid+d+hi
NK007(ja)001:5118: h'u +aah sarba sid+d+hi h'u +aah bcom ldan 'das 'jam
NK007(ja)001:5119: dpal dmar po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa'i sku
NK007(ja)001:5120: gsung thugs yon tan phrin las mi zad pa rgyan
NK007(ja)001:5121: gyi 'khor lo'i dngos grub rgya mtsho la mnga' brnyes
NK007(ja)001:5122: par gyur cig / a la la hoh su ka sid+d+hi zhes brjod do //
NK007(ja)001:5123: ma h+aa m+aam sa rol pas khams gsum dbang du bsdud par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5124: dza gad dpa' bo la rol pas 'gro ba ma
NK007(ja)001:5125: lus 'dul bar gyur cig rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas
NK007(ja)001:5126: 'jam dpal gyi sku tshe dang lang tsho la mnga'
NK007(ja)001:5128: zla rgyas dang zla phrom la rol pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5129: 'jam des rol pas dgongs pa chos nyid kyi klong la nyams pa med par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5132: kun tu rgyu la rol bas dgra bgegs tshar gcod par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5133: a la la hoh su ka sid+d+hi /
NK007(ja)001:5134: de nas bsgrub pa'i mjug bsdu ba la /
NK007(ja)001:5135: gtor mas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5136: lhag ma'i cho ga rgyas par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5137: smon lam gyis mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5139: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK007(ja)001:5140: skye 'gag med pa'i chos nyid klong brdal ba'i //
NK007(ja)001:5141: 'jam dbyangs lha tshogs bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5142: bdag gis sgo gsum g.yo sgyu ma mchis pas //
NK007(ja)001:5143: dad dang dam tshig brtson 'grus lhur blangs te //
NK007(ja)001:5144: lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor 'di bris nas //
NK007(ja)001:5145: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag gzhung bzhin mthar phyin pas //
NK007(ja)001:5146: lhag pa'i ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor mthar phyin cing //
NK007(ja)001:5147: byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor mngon rdzogs te //
NK007(ja)001:5148: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor chen por bsgrub pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5149: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub par shog /
NK007(ja)001:5150: b+han+d+ha'i rdzas mchog mtshan ldan la brten nas //
NK007(ja)001:5151: bsnyen bsgrub rnam bzhi tshul bzhin bgyis pa yis //
NK007(ja)001:5152: sa dang lam lnga'i sgrib pa kun byang nas //
NK007(ja)001:5153: sems nyid yi dam lha ru yongs smin te //
NK007(ja)001:5154: phung po'i rgya mdud 'di dag rnam grol tshe //
NK007(ja)001:5155: 'phags mchog 'jam pa'i dbyangs su 'tshar rgya shog /
NK007(ja)001:5156: rig 'dzin gsum gyi sa la sgrib sbyong nas //
NK007(ja)001:5157: rgyal ba sku gsum rgya mtsho byed pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5158: sku gsum 'khor ba dag pa'i chos 'chad cing //
NK007(ja)001:5159: rgyud dag sangs rgyas sku dang dbyer med shog /
NK007(ja)001:5160: dkyil 'khor lha la mar me 'di phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5161: snang ba'i sgo 'byed zhun mar mdangs ldan 'dis //
NK007(ja)001:5162: ye shes snang ba chen po'i shul mtshon nas //
NK007(ja)001:5163: sa dang lam la rim dang gcig char du //
NK007(ja)001:5164: mi shes rmongs pa'i dri ma rab bsal nas //
NK007(ja)001:5165: thams cad mkhyen pa'i ye shes thob pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5166: dbyer med kun bzang sa la mthar phyin shog /
NK007(ja)001:5167: dkyil 'khor lha la bdud rtsi 'di phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5168: nyon mongs gcong rnying nad las rab thar te //
NK007(ja)001:5169: dug lnga'i nad kun ye shes lngar gyur nas //
NK007(ja)001:5170: 'chi med bdud rtsi chos kyi sku thob shog /
NK007(ja)001:5171: dkyil 'khor lha la gtor ma 'di phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5172: nyon mongs 'phongs pa'i sdug bsngal rab bsal nas //
NK007(ja)001:5173: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la longs spyod cing //
NK007(ja)001:5174: rgyal ba longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku thob shog /
NK007(ja)001:5175: dkyil 'khor lha la rak+ta 'di phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5176: nyon mongs chags pa'i srid pa kun sbyangs te //
NK007(ja)001:5177: zag med bde ba phun sum tshogs 'gyur nas //
NK007(ja)001:5178: sprul pa'i sku thob 'gro don mthar phyin shog /
NK007(ja)001:5179: dkyil 'khor lha la tshogs mchod cher phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5180: brel 'phongs dbul ba'i nad las rab thar te //
NK007(ja)001:5181: 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po'i longs spyod ltar //
NK007(ja)001:5182: rgyal srid de bzhin gshegs ltar dbang bsgyur shog /
NK007(ja)001:5183: dkyil 'khor lha la ta na mchod 'bul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5184: skye 'gag med par thugs rje'i rol pa yis //
NK007(ja)001:5185: skye shi med par 'khor ba brtsad bcad nas //
NK007(ja)001:5186: srid pa dong sprugs thams cad 'tshang rgya shog /
NK007(ja)001:5187: dkyil 'khor lha la ga na 'di phul bas //
NK007(ja)001:5188: bde chen klong du chags sred rab sbyangs te //
NK007(ja)001:5189: zag med rgyal ba'i bde ba gdugs brdal zhing //
NK007(ja)001:5190: 'du 'bral med par kun bzang sku thob shog /
NK007(ja)001:5191: dkyil 'khor lha la bla bre yol ba dang //
NK007(ja)001:5192: gdugs dang rgyal mtshan 'phan phran la sogs pa //
NK007(ja)001:5193: dur khrod rgyan rnams rab tu phul ba yis //
NK007(ja)001:5194: gang zhig zhi bas 'dul bar ma gyur la //
NK007(ja)001:5195: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK007(ja)001:5196: 'bar ba'i sku la dur khrod rab brgyan pa'i //
NK007(ja)001:5197: longs spyod rdzogs pa khro bo'i skur bstan nas //
NK007(ja)001:5198: drag shul thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul ba dang //
NK007(ja)001:5199: 'khor ba'i gdung ba skyob cing 'dren pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5200: mi nub rgyal mtshan g.yul las rnam par rgyal //
NK007(ja)001:5201: shes rab thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dren pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5202: thugs rje'i chen pos 'gro don rdzogs byas nas //
NK007(ja)001:5203: rgyal ba'i sku lnga gsung lnga thugs lnga dang //
NK007(ja)001:5204: yon tan lnga dang phrin las de bzhin te //
NK007(ja)001:5205: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo thob gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5207: chos nyid zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos par /
NK007(ja)001:5208: sku 'bar ba chen po'i cha lugs kyis /
NK007(ja)001:5209: gdug pa can tshar gcod pa dang 'gro ba rnams bla na med par 'dren pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5210: chos nyid kyi phyag rgya las mdzad pa shin tu khros pas /
NK007(ja)001:5211: 'jam dpal dmar po'i lha tshogs rnams thugs rje'i ngang gis mkhyen pa mdzad cing dgongs su gsol /
NK007(ja)001:5212: snang srid thams cad ni dkyil 'khor /
NK007(ja)001:5213: 'byor pa thams cad ni longs spyod /
NK007(ja)001:5214: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtsho phul bas /
NK007(ja)001:5216: bdag dang sems can thams cad rdo rje 'chang gi sa thob nas /
NK007(ja)001:5217: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa la mthar phyin par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5218: hoh phyi nang snod bcud kyi bsdus pa'i chos thams
NK007(ja)001:5219: cad 'jam dpal dmar po'i dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis
NK007(ja)001:5221: bdag dang mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad sku
NK007(ja)001:5222: gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du phyir mi ldog pa
NK007(ja)001:5223: thob nas / ma h+aa su ka bde ba chen por lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5224: hoh 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos
NK007(ja)001:5225: thams cad rang gi sems yin pas phyogs ris med
NK007(ja)001:5226: pa rang byung gi ye shes su klong brdal /
NK007(ja)001:5227: phyi nang med pa chos nyid klong du rang shar /
NK007(ja)001:5230: bzang ngan dang blang dor med /
NK007(ja)001:5231: skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur med par thig le chen
NK007(ja)001:5232: po'i klong du gdal bas 'khor ba sangs rgyas su
NK007(ja)001:5233: dong sprugs / sdug bsngal chos nyid du la bzla /
NK007(ja)001:5234: rnam rtog ye shes su dbang bsgyur /
NK007(ja)001:5235: rgyud drug bde chen du rgyas gdab /
NK007(ja)001:5236: mtho dman klong chen du khod snyoms /
NK007(ja)001:5237: skye shi dang 'pho 'gyur med par rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'das /
NK007(ja)001:5238: sems can ye nas sangs rgyas su gdal bas /
NK007(ja)001:5239: don 'di tshig tsam brjod pa las rtogs pa klong du gyur na lta ci smos te /
NK007(ja)001:5240: zur tsam thos pa tsam gyis kyang 'tshang mi rgya ba'i dbang med de sangs rgyas par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5241: rgyal ba'i bka' lung gi snying khu 'dis /
NK007(ja)001:5242: bdag dang sems can thams cad zab mo'i don 'di mthar phyin nas /
NK007(ja)001:5243: gsang don zab mo 'di snod ngan la mi spel /
NK007(ja)001:5244: nges par 'bras bu mi bslu ba thob /
NK007(ja)001:5245: bka' yi gnyer blang nas kun tu bzang po dbye
NK007(ja)001:5246: ba med pa'i sa la mngon par 'tshar rgya bar
NK007(ja)001:5247: gyur cig / de nas bum pa'i steng gi b+han+d+ha lcang lo blangs la /
NK007(ja)001:5248: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la gtang rag gtong ngo //
NK007(ja)001:5249: de nas phyi rol du mkha' 'gro ma bskyang /
NK007(ja)001:5250: nang du log la tshe bstim /
NK007(ja)001:5254: rgyun ting la gnas par bya /
NK007(ja)001:5261: rdo rje lhun grub rtsal chen ngas //
NK007(ja)001:5262: phug lung nag po'i dur khrod du //
NK007(ja)001:5263: 'jam dpal dmar pos lung bstan nas //
NK007(ja)001:5264: rgya 'chad bang so dmar po nas //
NK007(ja)001:5265: rgyud sde mang po'i bcud phyung ba //
NK007(ja)001:5266: bka' yi sgrub lung zab mo 'di //
NK007(ja)001:5267: ma ru rtse yi zhal bgros nas //
NK007(ja)001:5269: dbang lung rdzogs shing snod ldan pas //
NK007(ja)001:5270: shi theb gcig las spel re kan //
NK007(ja)001:5271: rgya gar d+ha na da las yon tan rgya mtsho la /
NK007(ja)001:5272: tshe snga ma'i spun zlar dgongs nas gtad do //
NK007(ja)001:5275: shin tu zab pas sbas rgya /
NK007(ja)001:5280: // // 'gro mgon dar ma seng ge'i zhal gdams /
NK007(ja)001:5281: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed dmar po'i rgyun khyer yi dam nar ma bzhugs so //
NK007(ja)001:5282: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal dma' po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK007(ja)001:5283: 'di nyid kyi dal du dbang rdzogs par thob cing /
NK007(ja)001:5284: dam tshig dang sdom pa ldan pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK007(ja)001:5285: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'dod pas /
NK007(ja)001:5286: mngon par rtogs pa bsgom pa'i rim pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5287: mchod pa'i go rim la gsum ste /
NK007(ja)001:5291: bris sku rab gnas dang ldan pa bkram /
NK007(ja)001:5292: sman raka gtor gsum mchod pa rnams pa lnga bshams /
NK007(ja)001:5294: dang po sngon 'gro la bdun las /
NK007(ja)001:5295: dang po mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5296: stong pa'i ngang las rang nyid gshin rje'i gshed dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK007(ja)001:5298: g.yon sdigs mdzub las me 'bar ba /
NK007(ja)001:5299: dur khrod kyi rgyan gyis brgyan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5300: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad sprul pa'i khro chung gis gtams par gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5302: gsang sngags don la mi mos shing //
NK007(ja)001:5303: theg pa'i don la mi dad pa //
NK007(ja)001:5305: so so rang rang gnas su dengs //
NK007(ja)001:5306: +amo h+r+aihsh+ti wish+ti t+aa na na wa ra tsakra a pa na ya h'u h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5307: +amo b+h+r+aum h'u b+h+r+aum t+r+aam b+h+r+aum h+r+aihb+h+r+aum h+aa b+h+r+aum /
NK007(ja)001:5309: ba spu dang shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas khro chung
NK007(ja)001:5310: mtshon cha thogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang
NK007(ja)001:5317: rdo rje rgya gram rnams 'phros pas /
NK007(ja)001:5319: tshur 'dus pas ra gur du gyur nas /
NK007(ja)001:5320: bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5322: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah h'u /
NK007(ja)001:5323: 'jam dpal 'khor bcas gsan cing dgongs su gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5324: bdag cag ma rig lus dang ngag sems kyis //
NK007(ja)001:5325: bag med tshul gyis dam las 'gal gyur te //
NK007(ja)001:5326: 'jam dpal lha tshogs thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK007(ja)001:5327: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5329: gsum pa brda' sgo dbye ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5331: dbang drag 'bar ba'i pho brang dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK007(ja)001:5332: 'jug par 'tshal bas phyogs bzhi'i sgo bzhi po //
NK007(ja)001:5333: me long mnyam nyid sor rtog bya grub bzhi'i //
NK007(ja)001:5334: byams pa'i zhal bzang bstan phyir sgo phyes shig /
NK007(ja)001:5335: b+h+r+aum man+da la pra be sha ya phata /
NK007(ja)001:5336: bzhi pa brda phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5338: dbang drag 'bar ba'i pho brang gzhal yas na //
NK007(ja)001:5339: 'jam dbyangs khro bo 'jam dpal gshin rje'i lha //
NK007(ja)001:5340: thugs kyi sras mchog gshin rje ma ru rtse //
NK007(ja)001:5341: 'khor dang bcas la sgo gsum dang bas 'dud //
NK007(ja)001:5342: brda yi mchod 'bul gar 'di bzhes su gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5343: ya ma a ti p+au hoh pra t+ai ts+tsha hoh lnga pa dam bca' ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5345: bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol nas //
NK007(ja)001:5346: lha mchog gshin rje'i gshed dang smon lam mthun bsdebs pas //
NK007(ja)001:5347: dus 'dir zhal mthong yi dam lhar gsol gyis //
NK007(ja)001:5348: lha mchog khyed kyis bdag la byin gyis rlobs //
NK007(ja)001:5349: bdag kyang ting 'dzin rtse gcig mi gtong gis //
NK007(ja)001:5350: khyed kyi thugs rjes bdag yongs ma gtong cig /
NK007(ja)001:5352: drug pa byin dbab cing mchod pa brlab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5354: gru gsum dmar nag rol pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK007(ja)001:5355: 'jam dpal gshin rje dmar po ral pa can //
NK007(ja)001:5356: 'jig rten khams rnams kun la mnga' mdzad pa //
NK007(ja)001:5357: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di la byin phob cig /
NK007(ja)001:5358: sngon tshe gong nas bsnyen cing sgrub pa'i lha //
NK007(ja)001:5359: bcom ldan dpal chen 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed //
NK007(ja)001:5360: khyod kyis bdag la byin chen dbab tu gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5361: khyed kyis bdag la dbang chen bskur du gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5362: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK007(ja)001:5371: mchod pa'i lha mo dpag tu med par gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5372: +amo +aa h'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah
NK007(ja)001:5373: ka p+aa la ye shes kyi bdud rtsis khengs par
NK007(ja)001:5374: gyur / +amo ma h+aa ba lim ta te dzo
NK007(ja)001:5375: ba lim ta ba la ba te gu h+ya sa
NK007(ja)001:5377: mchod gtor 'dod yon gyi lha mo dang /
NK007(ja)001:5378: bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5379: +amo rak+ta dz+wa la sa mu tra man+da la h'u /
NK007(ja)001:5380: rak+ta khrag gi rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5381: m+aam sa rak+ta kem ni ri ti /
NK007(ja)001:5382: las gtor sha khrag rus pa'i phung por gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5383: de nas bdun pa yan lag dgu pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5384: mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma brgyud pa yi dam lha tshogs bzhugs par gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5385: badz+ra sa ma ya dzah 'jam dpal rdo rje la sogs pa'i //
NK007(ja)001:5386: rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa la //
NK007(ja)001:5387: lus ngag yid gsum gus ldan pas //
NK007(ja)001:5388: kun nas dang bas phyag 'tshal lo //
NK007(ja)001:5389: sangs rgyas zhing du gang basngagasa pa'i //
NK007(ja)001:5390: 'jig rten dag na mchog gyur pa //
NK007(ja)001:5391: rin chen me tog bdug spos sogs //
NK007(ja)001:5392: kun nas sprul te mchod par bgyi //
NK007(ja)001:5393: bdag gis sngon nas bsags pa'i sdig /
NK007(ja)001:5394: kun nas bsags par gyur pa rnams //
NK007(ja)001:5395: rang bzhin med kyang yod tshul gyis //
NK007(ja)001:5396: mgon po kun gyi spyan sngar bshags //
NK007(ja)001:5397: mgon po kun gyi bsod nams dang //
NK007(ja)001:5398: dman pa'i dge ba thams cad la //
NK007(ja)001:5399: de bzhin mthun pa'i lhag sems kyis //
NK007(ja)001:5400: dang bas rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK007(ja)001:5401: bde gshegs byang chub mchog brnyes nas //
NK007(ja)001:5403: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba la //
NK007(ja)001:5404: tshangs pa bzhin du gsol ba 'debs //
NK007(ja)001:5405: mya ngan 'da' bzhed de dag la //
NK007(ja)001:5406: 'gro kun yun du bde ba'i phyir //
NK007(ja)001:5407: ji srid 'khor ba de srid du //
NK007(ja)001:5408: mya ngan mi 'da' bzhugs su gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5409: ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs par //
NK007(ja)001:5410: bdag gi dge ba de bzhin du //
NK007(ja)001:5411: kun nas zad par ma gyur bas //
NK007(ja)001:5412: sems can yongs su smin par shog /
NK007(ja)001:5413: bdag kyang dus 'di phan chad nas //
NK007(ja)001:5414: byang chub snying por mchis kyi bar //
NK007(ja)001:5416: thugs rjes yongs su bzung bar mdzod //
NK007(ja)001:5417: dus 'di nas ni bzungs nas ni //
NK007(ja)001:5418: mgon po khyod kyi bka' bzhin du //
NK007(ja)001:5419: sems can kun don bsgrub lags kyis //
NK007(ja)001:5420: byin gyis rlabs par mdzad du gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5422: mdun gyi nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'i bla ma yi
NK007(ja)001:5423: dam rnams kyi gnas gsum nas 'od zer dkar dmar
NK007(ja)001:5424: mthing gsum dpag tu med pa 'phros /
NK007(ja)001:5425: rang gi gnas gsum du thim /
NK007(ja)001:5427: de nas lha rnams 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas /
NK007(ja)001:5429: de'i 'od zer gyis phyi nang snod bcud thams cad 'od du zhu /
NK007(ja)001:5430: 'od de slar 'dus thig le dmar po gyur pa'i ngang du sems mnyam par bzhag go //
NK007(ja)001:5432: dang po bskyed rim bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5433: rang rig snang stong dbyer med kyi rang bzhin yi ge h'u dmar po gsal ba las /
NK007(ja)001:5434: e yam ram bam kem ram rnams rim par chad 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK007(ja)001:5435: e las nam mkha' mthing nag gru gsum /
NK007(ja)001:5436: yam las rlung rdo rje rgya gram ljang gu /
NK007(ja)001:5437: ram las rak+ta'i rgya mtsho zlum po /
NK007(ja)001:5438: bam las zhing chen gyi sa gzhi smug po /
NK007(ja)001:5439: kem las rus pa'i ri rab /
NK007(ja)001:5440: ram las me dpung dmar po gru gsum gyi steng du /
NK007(ja)001:5441: b+h+r+aum smug nag las 'od zer 'phro 'dus zhu ba las /
NK007(ja)001:5442: gzhal yas khang thod pa skam rlon las grub pa /
NK007(ja)001:5443: dbyibs grub bzhi dbus su gru gsum dmar po zlu gam kyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5444: thod pa skam po'i mu khyud /
NK007(ja)001:5446: rdo rje'i ra ba mthing ga /
NK007(ja)001:5449: thod pa tshar gsum gyi rtsig pa /
NK007(ja)001:5450: gnam lcags kyi gzer gtab cing rak+tasa sbyar ba /
NK007(ja)001:5458: phyogs skyong ba'i lpags pa'i thog /
NK007(ja)001:5462: sbrul gyi d+r+wa ba d+r+wa phyed /
NK007(ja)001:5463: gra bzhir zhing gi rgyal mtshan bzhi phyar ba /
NK007(ja)001:5464: phyi rol du dur khrod chen po gnas brgyad /
NK007(ja)001:5465: rdo rje me ri dang bcas pas bskor ba'i gzhal
NK007(ja)001:5466: yas khang gi dbus su bdud dang srin po thams
NK007(ja)001:5467: cad dang gshin rje pho mo byi chings su bsnol
NK007(ja)001:5468: ba'i steng du / ma he glang rgod pho mo bardzisa pa'i khri stengs su /
NK007(ja)001:5469: pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la rgyu'i yi ge h'u dmar po babs /
NK007(ja)001:5470: de las 'od zer 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK007(ja)001:5471: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya m+aan+ta ka ma ru rtse be ta li h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5473: rang nyid skad cig gis 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed
NK007(ja)001:5474: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog pad+ma r+aa ga'i mdog
NK007(ja)001:5475: ltar dmar ba / phyag g.yas pa thod dbyug rdo rjes mtshan pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5476: me'i 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa 'od dang bcas pa 'phyar zhing /
NK007(ja)001:5477: g.yon rlung gi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa bsnams pa /
NK007(ja)001:5478: spyan g.yas pa las me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:5479: spyan g.yon pa las las kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:5480: shangs nas bskal ba'i rlung nag 'tshub cing /
NK007(ja)001:5481: smrin ma dang ag tshom dmar ser las bskal pa'i me stag 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:5482: zhal bgrad cing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK007(ja)001:5483: mche ba g.yas pa las rak+ta'i chu rgyun 'bab cing /
NK007(ja)001:5484: mche ba g.yon pa las ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK007(ja)001:5485: lcags kyu lta bus dgra bgegs kyi tsit+ta 'dren pa
NK007(ja)001:5486: / dbu skra kham nag 'khyil ba'i skra gseb nas /
NK007(ja)001:5487: sprul pa'i khro chung mang po 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:5488: ral pa'i rtse la b+han+d+ha lcang los brgyan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5489: sku stod la zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK007(ja)001:5490: glang chen gyi sko rlon gsol zhing /
NK007(ja)001:5491: sku smad la stag gi sham thabs gsol ba /
NK007(ja)001:5492: thod skam lnga yis dbu rgyan dang /
NK007(ja)001:5493: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa bzhi'i do shal /
NK007(ja)001:5494: sbrul rigs lnga'i snyan cha dbu rgyan mgur chu do shal dpung rgyan ske rags rnams byas pa /
NK007(ja)001:5495: khrag zhag thal ba'i mtshan ma can /
NK007(ja)001:5496: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum du brjid pa'i tshul gyis bzhugs
NK007(ja)001:5497: shing zhal nas h'u dang phata kyi sgra sgrog pa
NK007(ja)001:5498: / me dpung dmar nag 'bar ba'i dbus na bzhugs pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5499: trag rak+sha ma ma e ka dz+aa ti dza dzah
NK007(ja)001:5500: de'i pang na yum e ka dz+aa ti sku mdog
NK007(ja)001:5501: dmar smug zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas kha t+wam bsnams
NK007(ja)001:5504: re lde'i sham thabs dang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan cing /
NK007(ja)001:5505: 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis gtso bo la blta zhing sbyor bas dgyes par bskyed pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5506: gtso bo'i spyan dang shangs ljags thugs ka ste gnas
NK007(ja)001:5507: bzhi nas dzahdamara po bzhi 'khor lo'i rtsibs steng du
NK007(ja)001:5508: 'phros pas / shar du dri za pho mo bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK007(ja)001:5509: pra ma r+aa dza ni dzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:5510: srin po ma ru rtse g.yas spu gri dang g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa yum dang sbyor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5511: 'khor du srin po mi zan 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:5512: lhor gshin rje pho mo bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK007(ja)001:5513: ya ma r+aa dza ni dzah zhes pas gshin rje ma ru rtse g.yas dbyug to dang /
NK007(ja)001:5514: g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa yum dang sbyor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5515: 'khor gshin rje mi zan 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:5516: nub tu dmu bdud pho mo bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK007(ja)001:5517: d+ha sha g+hi wa dzah zhes pas bdud po ma ru rtse g.yas ral gri /
NK007(ja)001:5518: g.yon thod khrag dang zhags pa 'dzin pa yum dang sbyor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5519: 'khor du bdud po mi zan 'bum gyis bskor ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:5520: byang du gnod sbyin pho mo'i steng du /
NK007(ja)001:5521: ku be r+aa dza ni dzah zhes pas gnod sbyin ma ru rtse g.yas be con dang /
NK007(ja)001:5522: g.yon thod khrag dang zhags pa 'dzin pa yum dang sbyor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5523: 'khor gnod sbyin mi zan 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5524: yab yum thams cad shin tu khros pa'i cha lugs
NK007(ja)001:5525: can sku mdog dmar po dur khrod kyi chas kyis
NK007(ja)001:5526: brgyan pa'o // gtso bo'i yan lag bzhi las /
NK007(ja)001:5527: ma dmar po bzhi rtsibs mchan bzhir 'phros pas /
NK007(ja)001:5529: shar lhor mar khu'i mtsho nang du bdud kyi gdan
NK007(ja)001:5530: la rdo rje ya byin ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK007(ja)001:5531: g.yas rdo rje g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa /
NK007(ja)001:5532: 'khor du bdud mo 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5534: lho nub tu sbrang rtsi'i mtshor gza' yi gdan la
NK007(ja)001:5535: rdo rje de byin ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas
NK007(ja)001:5536: rin chen / g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa'i 'khor du gza' yi bu mo 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5538: nub byang khrag zhag gi mtsho la btsan gyi gdan
NK007(ja)001:5539: la rdo rje bswe byin ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis
NK007(ja)001:5540: g.yas pad+ma / g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa'i 'khor du btsan gyi bu mo 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5542: byang shar du 'o ma'i mtsho la klu'i gdan la
NK007(ja)001:5543: rdo rje phag byin ma zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas
NK007(ja)001:5544: rgya gram / g.yon thod khrag 'dzin pa'i 'khor du klu'i bu mo 'bum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:5545: thams cad kyang sku mdog dmar po dang ldan pa
NK007(ja)001:5546: khro mo'i cha lugs can dur khrod kyi chas kyis
NK007(ja)001:5547: brgyan pa'o // gzhan yang bar khyams la ging chen bco brgyad /
NK007(ja)001:5548: sku mdog dmar po g.yas ral gri 'phyar zhing /
NK007(ja)001:5549: g.yon tsit+ta bsnams pa khros 'khrugs rngams pa'i tshul can /
NK007(ja)001:5550: sgo bzhir bswe yi skyes bu bzhi /
NK007(ja)001:5551: sku mdog dmar po bswe khrab dang bswe rmog gsol zhing bswe'i bya khral chibs pa /
NK007(ja)001:5552: g.yas lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu bsnams shing /
NK007(ja)001:5553: g.yon pa dgra snying spar gyis 'debs pa /
NK007(ja)001:5554: dur khrod brgyad du khram thogs bdud /
NK007(ja)001:5557: las gshin bye ba ther 'bum dang bcas pa bzhugs pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5558: gnyis pa dbang bskur zhing spyan drangs ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5559: lha thams cad kyi dpral bar +amo las rnam snang /
NK007(ja)001:5561: thugs kar h'u las mi bskyod pa rnams kyis mtshan par bsam la /
NK007(ja)001:5562: +amo +aa kro te ka ya m+aan+ta ka k+aa ya /
NK007(ja)001:5565: dbu rgyan thod pa'i khang bu lngar rgyal ba rigs lngas dbu brgyan par bsam la /
NK007(ja)001:5566: b+han+d+ha ka p+aa la tram tram /
NK007(ja)001:5567: h'u +amo s+w+aa +aam h+aah bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK007(ja)001:5568: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang che /
NK007(ja)001:5569: dmar nag gru gsum 'bar ba'i gzhal yas nas /
NK007(ja)001:5570: 'jam dpal dmar po 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs /
NK007(ja)001:5571: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan /
NK007(ja)001:5572: many+dzu sh+r+ai ya m+aan+ta ka man+da la a gats+tsha ya /
NK007(ja)001:5573: sa ma ya h'u dzah dzahmh'u bam ho /
NK007(ja)001:5576: gsum pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5578: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK007(ja)001:5579: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5580: sbyor sgrol rak+ta'i mchod pas mchod //
NK007(ja)001:5581: thugs rjes dgongs la bzhes su gsol //
NK007(ja)001:5583: mthun pa'i dam rdzas nyer spyod 'dod yon lnga //
NK007(ja)001:5584: sha khrag rus pa dug lnga'i mchod pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5585: khrag sna dgu dang mtsho chen bzhi rnams dang //
NK007(ja)001:5586: bstan pa 'jig pa'i dgra bgegs mchod par bzhes //
NK007(ja)001:5587: rnal 'byor bcol ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK007(ja)001:5588: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dza ma ma e
NK007(ja)001:5589: ka dz+aa ti dzah dzah a nu r+au pa kh+aa
NK007(ja)001:5590: hi / su ru pa kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5591: ta ku pa tra mi ta kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5592: ku pa ra tsan+da kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5593: sgrol ging bdag po ma ru rtse yi zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5594: dam can sngags kyi srung ma e ka dz+aa ti'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5595: srog zan gyi shan pa ma ru rtse'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5596: bswe mo snying zan ma'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5597: bswe yi skyes bu bzhi'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5598: 'khor gyi bshan pa lag ring bzhi'i zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5599: sgrol ging bco brgyad zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5600: khram thogs bdun kyi zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5601: zhags thogs btsan gyi zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5602: las gshin bye ba ther 'bum gyi zhal du kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5603: ma h+aa m+aam sa la kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5609: pany+tsa a mri ta kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5610: ma h+aa ba lim ta kh+aa hi /
NK007(ja)001:5611: zhes gsum mam bdun gyi 'bul lo //
NK007(ja)001:5613: rang 'jam dpal dmar po gsal ba'i thugs ka'i h'u
NK007(ja)001:5614: la sngags phreng gis bskor ba las 'od zer dmar
NK007(ja)001:5615: po 'phros / snod bcud thams cad gzhal yas khang dang lhar gsal la sngags bzlas so //
NK007(ja)001:5616: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ku m+aa ra ya ma r+aa dza h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5617: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dza ma ma e
NK007(ja)001:5618: ka dz+aa ti dza dzah zhes gang 'grub bzlas la
NK007(ja)001:5621: se gol bsnol mar gdab cing /
NK007(ja)001:5623: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa rnams dang /
NK007(ja)001:5624: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed dmar po'i
NK007(ja)001:5625: lha tshogs rnams mkhyen par mdzad cing bdag la dgongs
NK007(ja)001:5626: su gsol / bdag gi rgyal ba'i bka' bden pa 'di 'grub par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5627: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5628: bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung bar gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5629: sems can don du 'jam dpal dmar po'i go 'phang thob par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5630: thob nas kyang sems can kyi don bsam gyis mi khyab pa byed par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5631: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phrin las thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:5634: dge ba 'di yis myur du bdag /
NK007(ja)001:5636: 'gro ba gcig kyang ma lus pa //
NK007(ja)001:5637: de yi sa la 'god par shog /
NK007(ja)001:5638: ces brjod spros pa la dga' na /
NK007(ja)001:5640: bsdus pa la dga' na rgyun gyi yi dam nar ma 'di ltar /
NK007(ja)001:5641: bsgom pa dang bzlas pa gtso bor bya ba 'di /
NK007(ja)001:5642: 'gro mgon dar ma seng ge'i zhal gdams rim par brgyud pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5645: // // bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed dmar po'i phrin las kyi sgom khog bzhugs so //
NK007(ja)001:5646: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal dmar po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK007(ja)001:5647: 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed kyi mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob par 'dod pas /
NK007(ja)001:5648: mngon pa'i rtogs pa bsgom pa'i rim pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5649: mchod pa'i go rim bstan pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5655: gzhi phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan par bya ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:5656: bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa'i rim pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5657: sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga dngos so //
NK007(ja)001:5658: dang po phun sum tshogs pa la lnga las /
NK007(ja)001:5659: dang po gnas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5660: spyir sngon gyi grub pa thob pas zhabs kyis bcags pa byin rlabs dang ldan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5667: gzhung las bshad pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5669: nam mkha' 'khor lo rtsibs chags pa //
NK007(ja)001:5671: phu na dar dkar yul bres pa //
NK007(ja)001:5672: mda' na g.yu yi man+dala yod //
NK007(ja)001:5673: shar ri g.yel zhig lho ri gzhol //
NK007(ja)001:5674: nub ri mtho la byang ri skyob //
NK007(ja)001:5675: snga dro nyi ma'i mdangs bsdud cing //
NK007(ja)001:5676: dgong mo nyi ma'i zer bsdud pa //
NK007(ja)001:5677: rtsi shing nags tshal me tog rgyas //
NK007(ja)001:5678: chu bo dal zhing gnod pa med //
NK007(ja)001:5679: skye bo'i ya ga spangs pa yi //
NK007(ja)001:5680: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i gnas mchog tu //
NK007(ja)001:5681: bar chad bsal ba'i cho ga bya //
NK007(ja)001:5683: khyad par du dur khrod chen po mi ro gsar rnying yod pa'am /
NK007(ja)001:5684: yang na brag dmar chol bzang 'dra ba /
NK007(ja)001:5685: shing rtsi gdug pa can 'khrungs pa /
NK007(ja)001:5686: khra dang 'ug pa'i tshang yod pa /
NK007(ja)001:5687: 'dre srin gdug pa can gnas pa de lta bur bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5689: gnas ni dur khrod chen po yi //
NK007(ja)001:5690: mi ro gsar rnying yod pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5691: shin tu 'jigs shing skyi g.ya' ba //
NK007(ja)001:5693: yang na brag dmar mche ris can //
NK007(ja)001:5694: rtsi shing nags tshal drungs 'thug pa //
NK007(ja)001:5695: gsod byed khra yi tshang bcas pa //
NK007(ja)001:5696: gnod sbyin drag po 'du ba'i gnas //
NK007(ja)001:5697: der ni dkyil 'khor rab tu bya //
NK007(ja)001:5699: yang na rang dbang zhing nyams dga' ba'am /
NK007(ja)001:5700: mkhar chen po'i sum thog tu bya bar yang gsungs so //
NK007(ja)001:5701: gnyis pa sgrub pa po phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5702: rnal 'byor pa mi chos kyi rgyu dag pa /
NK007(ja)001:5703: dad pa che zhing brtson 'grus dang ldan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5704: shes rab che zhing snying rje dang ldan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5705: bsgom bsran che zhing snying rus che ba dang ldan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5706: dam tshig gtsang zhing brtul zhugs dang ldan pa /
NK007(ja)001:5707: bla ma bzang zhing thugs kyis zin pa /
NK007(ja)001:5708: dbang rdzogs shing man ngag dang ldan pas bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5711: shes rab snying rje ldan pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5712: bsgom bsran che zhing 'gyur ba med //
NK007(ja)001:5713: dam tshig 'jig pa'i mkhar ltar bsrung //
NK007(ja)001:5714: thog mar bla ma bsten byas te //
NK007(ja)001:5715: dbang dang man ngag ldan par bya //
NK007(ja)001:5717: gsum pa 'khor phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5718: dgyes pa skong ba'i 'khor gzungs ma mtshan dang ldan pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5719: thugs thub dpa' bo'i 'khor blo brtan zhing bka' blo bde ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:5720: rdul phyags skyes bu'i 'khor bsgo ba nyan cing don grub pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:5721: gzhan yang dge sbyor gyi grogs su 'gro ba ci rigs pa bsten cing /
NK007(ja)001:5722: gnod byed 'gal rkyen du gyur pa rnams spang bar bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5724: phyag rgya mtshan dang ldan pa dang //
NK007(ja)001:5725: grogs po dpa' la sems stobs ldan //
NK007(ja)001:5726: yid dang 'thad cing bsgo ba nyan //
NK007(ja)001:5728: bzhi pa dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5729: bsnyen pa dang bsgrub pa'i dus ni /
NK007(ja)001:5730: yar ngo'i tshes grangs dang gza' skar bzang po kho na la 'jug par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5731: drag po las sbyor gyi dus ni /
NK007(ja)001:5732: mar ngo'i dus su gza' skar ngan pa kho na la 'jug par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5734: bsnyen cing bsgrub pa yar gyi ngo //
NK007(ja)001:5735: tshes grangs gza' skar bzang la 'jug /
NK007(ja)001:5737: lnga pa rdzas phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5738: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad dang /
NK007(ja)001:5739: sgrub pa rten gyi yo byad dang /
NK007(ja)001:5740: rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad dang /
NK007(ja)001:5741: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad dang /
NK007(ja)001:5742: bar chad bsal ba'i yo byad rnams ldab thang du bsags par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5743: spyi don gnyis pa bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5746: chu gtor la sogs pa dge ba'i rtsa ba ci 'byor pa bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5747: gsum pa sngon du 'gro ba'i cho ga dngos ni gnyis te /
NK007(ja)001:5748: dang po rdzas dang yo byad bshams pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5749: bkol byang nas 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK007(ja)001:5754: dkyil 'khor bri ba la sogs par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5755: de ltar ma grub na man+dala byi dor byas la /
NK007(ja)001:5756: me tog gi tshom bu bkod /
NK007(ja)001:5757: bris sku la sogs pa sku gsung thugs kyi rten bkram /
NK007(ja)001:5758: nang gi mchod pa sman phud dang rak+ta dang gtor ma yang bshams /
NK007(ja)001:5759: phyi'i mchod pa sna lnga yang bsham /
NK007(ja)001:5760: bla bre la sogs pa'i rgyan yang ci 'byor bsham mo //
NK007(ja)001:5761: gnyis pa cho ga'i sngon du 'gro ba ni drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:5767: mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5770: bar chad kyi bgegs kyi mi tshugs pa'i phyir ro //
NK007(ja)001:5773: rnam par mi rtog pa'i mtshams ni /
NK007(ja)001:5774: stan bde ba la lus kyi 'dug stangs legs par bcas te /
NK007(ja)001:5775: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog pa'i ngang la yun ring du bsgom mo //
NK007(ja)001:5776: gnyis pa bgegs bskrad pa'i mtshams ni /
NK007(ja)001:5777: ma sur+ya man+da la zhes brjod pas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor h'u dmar pos mtshan pa gcig bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:5778: h'u de spro bsdus 'od du zhu nas /
NK007(ja)001:5779: +amo a kro te ka many+dzu sh+r+ai ya m+aa n+ta ka h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5780: ces brjod pas khro bo sku mdog dmar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK007(ja)001:5782: g.yon pa sdigs mdzub zhags pa dang bcas pa gcig
NK007(ja)001:5783: sku la dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan pa gcig
NK007(ja)001:5784: bsgom mo // de nas bgegs la bka' bsgo ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5786: gsang sngags don la zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod pas /
NK007(ja)001:5788: gsum pa sngags kyis bgegs bskrad pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5789: +amo h+r+aihsh+ti wish+ti t+aa zhes pa'i sngags brjod pas ba
NK007(ja)001:5790: spu dang shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas khro chung mtshon
NK007(ja)001:5791: cha thogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa 'phros te
NK007(ja)001:5792: bgegs rnams dpag tshad dang rgyang grags la sogs par
NK007(ja)001:5793: bskrad par bsam / bzhi pa ra ba dang gur gyi mtshams ni /
NK007(ja)001:5794: gong gi khro chung rnams slar 'dus te bskrad kyang
NK007(ja)001:5795: mi 'gro ba'i 'gegs rnams la mtshon cha'i char phab
NK007(ja)001:5796: ste / phung po rdul du brlag nas khro chung rnams ba spu'i bu gar thim par bsam pa'am /
NK007(ja)001:5797: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad khro bo'i gur du song bar bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:5798: de nas mtshon cha'i gur bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5799: lag pa'i sor mo lnga la dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsgom ste /
NK007(ja)001:5805: zhes sor mo rnams sprugs pas /
NK007(ja)001:5811: rdo rje rgya gram du gyur nas /
NK007(ja)001:5812: de rnams rim pa bzhin du steng nas gur dang /
NK007(ja)001:5816: bgegs a cang che bskal pa'i rlung gis kyang mi thar bar bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:5818: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtan bya'i phyir //
NK007(ja)001:5820: steng yang be con bla bre la //
NK007(ja)001:5821: zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:5822: lnga pa me dpung gi gur dang ra ba bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5823: mig g.yas pa ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la ram bsams te /
NK007(ja)001:5826: bskal pa'i me dpung chen por gyur nas /
NK007(ja)001:5827: bgegs kyi phung po thams cad bsreg cing /
NK007(ja)001:5828: steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad me dpung gis 'khrigs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5830: steng 'og phyogs mtshams zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:5831: drug pa sbyang zhing gsal ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5832: shangs la yam las rlung gi steng du h'u dmar po bsams te /
NK007(ja)001:5833: yam h'u zhes brjod pas ye shes kyi rlung chen por gyur nas /
NK007(ja)001:5834: bsregs pa'i thal ba rnams mi gnas par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5835: mig g.yon pa las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor steng du h'u dkar po bsams te /
NK007(ja)001:5836: de las ye shes kyi bdud rtsi byung nas /
NK007(ja)001:5837: dngos po'i ljan ljin thams cad bkrus /
NK007(ja)001:5838: bgegs kyi lus thams cad slar gsos nas byang chub kyi sems skyes te /
NK007(ja)001:5840: phyis mi byed par dam 'cha' zhing rang gi gnas su dengs par bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:5841: gnyis pa bshags pa bya ba ni gnyis te /
NK007(ja)001:5843: dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK007(ja)001:5844: gnyis pa dbye ba ni gsum ste /
NK007(ja)001:5845: dang po bshags pa'i rgyu ni /
NK007(ja)001:5846: gsang sngags kyi sgor zhugs nas rtsa ba dang yan
NK007(ja)001:5847: lag gi dam tshig nos pa las gzhung bzhin bsrung
NK007(ja)001:5848: ba rngo ma thogs te nongs pas so //
NK007(ja)001:5849: bshags pa byed pa'i rkyen ni nyams pa'i nyes dmigs byung ba'am /
NK007(ja)001:5850: dngos grub thob par 'dod pa'i phyir bshags pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5852: stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags te /
NK007(ja)001:5853: rten gyi stobs ni dkon mchog gi drung dang /
NK007(ja)001:5854: bla ma la sogs pa gang zag gi drung du'o //
NK007(ja)001:5856: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah zhes brjod cing se gol brdabs pas /
NK007(ja)001:5857: mdun gyi nam mkha' la bla ma dang yi dam
NK007(ja)001:5858: mkha' 'gro chos skyong la sogs pa spyan drangs te
NK007(ja)001:5861: sngar gyi nyes byas la 'gyod pa drag po zhe thag pa nas byas te /
NK007(ja)001:5862: tshig tu mthol zhing yid kyis bshags pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5864: phyis mi byed par dam 'cha' ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:5867: mchi ma 'khrugs te 'jam dpal dmar po 'khor bcas
NK007(ja)001:5868: zhes pa'i tshig nyi shu rtsa gcig gis spyir bshags
NK007(ja)001:5869: / rang rig ye shes zhes pa'i tshig bco brgyad kyis bye brag tu bshags pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5870: gsum pa brda' sgo dbye ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5872: b+h+r+aum las 'od zer gyi spro bsdus /
NK007(ja)001:5873: snod bcud sbyangs te mi dmigs pa las /
NK007(ja)001:5874: snang srid lha'i gzhal yas khang du gyur pas /
NK007(ja)001:5875: snod kyi 'jig rten ni gzhal yas khang /
NK007(ja)001:5876: bcud kyi sems can ni lha'i rang bzhin du bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:5877: ye shes kyi sgo bzhi nas zhugs te /
NK007(ja)001:5878: de lta bu'i dkyil 'khor du gsal bar bsgom pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:5880: dbang drag 'bar ba'i pho brang zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:5881: bzhi pa brda yi phyag bya ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:5882: lha dang gzhal yas khang de'ang yul gud pa ma yin te /
NK007(ja)001:5883: rang gi rig pa nyid snod bcud thams cad lha dang dkyil 'khor du gsal bar shar te /
NK007(ja)001:5884: don du na yul dang rig pa gnyis su med par mjal bas /
NK007(ja)001:5885: de ka khyad par gsang sngag kyi dgongs pa yin te /
NK007(ja)001:5886: ngom zhing ngo mtshar ba'i sgo nas brda phyag 'tshal te /
NK007(ja)001:5888: dbang drag 'bar ba'i pho brang zhes pa'i tshig lngas gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:5889: lnga pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5891: byin dbab pa gnyis su bzhed pa las /
NK007(ja)001:5892: gu ru pad+ma'i bzhed kyis dam bca' ba mi dgos gsungs nas dkyus las ma byung ste /
NK007(ja)001:5893: slob dpon d+ha na da la'i bzhed kyis /
NK007(ja)001:5894: dam bca' ba 'di phyag bzhes su mdzad de /
NK007(ja)001:5896: bskal pa dpag tu med pa'i sngon rol nas //
NK007(ja)001:5897: lha mchog gshin rje'i gshed dang smon lam mthun bsdebs nas //
NK007(ja)001:5898: dus 'dir zhal mthong yi dam lhar gsol gyis //
NK007(ja)001:5899: lha mchog khyed kyis bdag la byin gyis rlobs //
NK007(ja)001:5900: bdag cag ting 'dzin rtse gcig mi gtong gis //
NK007(ja)001:5901: khyod kyis thugs rjes bdag yongs ma btang zhig /
NK007(ja)001:5903: lag pa rdo rje rtse gcig pa'i phyag rgya dang bcas la /
NK007(ja)001:5904: tshig brjod pa dang mthun par yi dam du dam baca'o //
NK007(ja)001:5905: de nas byin dbab pa dngos ni /
NK007(ja)001:5907: zhes brjod rol mo'i sgra drag tu brdung zhing /
NK007(ja)001:5909: de ni bskyed pa zhes bya /
NK007(ja)001:5910: h'u bar pas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing thugs dam bskul /
NK007(ja)001:5911: de ni byin bsdu ba zhes bya /
NK007(ja)001:5912: h'u tha mas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa de la bstim pas /
NK007(ja)001:5914: de ni byin gyis dbab pa zhes bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5916: gru gsum dmar nag rol pa'i zhes tshig lngas gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:5917: drug pa mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5919: dang po thun mong gi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5920: dang po rdo rje dril bu brlab pa ste /
NK007(ja)001:5921: rdo rje mi dmigs pa las /
NK007(ja)001:5922: h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5923: de dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rang bzhin du bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:5925: zhes lan gsum du gsol la thugs kar bzung /
NK007(ja)001:5926: de nas dril bu mi dmigs pa las /
NK007(ja)001:5928: de dkyil 'khor gyi rang bzhin du bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:5930: zhes lan gsum du dkrol zhing lte bar bzung bar bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5931: rdo rje dril bu la thabs shes kyi dkyil 'khor la ngo sprod pa ni go sla'o //
NK007(ja)001:5932: thun mong gi mchod pa lnga po ni /
NK007(ja)001:5933: bdag yi dam gyi lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas h'u sngon po 'phros te /
NK007(ja)001:5934: bsang ba'i chu la thim pas bdud rtsi 'khyil bar bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5936: ces brjod cing nye reg dang 'thor 'thung bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:5937: yang thugs ka nas +aahdakara po 'phros te yon chab la thim pas /
NK007(ja)001:5938: lha mo dkar mo lag tu dung phor yon chab kyis bkang ba thogs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5942: d+h+au ser mo spros spos la thim /
NK007(ja)001:5943: lha mo spos khang thogs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5946: lha mo sngon mo me tog thogs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5947: ram dmar mo 'phros mar me la thim /
NK007(ja)001:5948: lha mo dmar mo mar me thogs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5951: lha mo ljang gu dri chab thogs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5952: de yang rang rang gi skabs su /
NK007(ja)001:5958: de nas gnyis pa khyad par gyi mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:5959: dang po rnge'u chung byin gyis brlabs te /
NK007(ja)001:5960: rnge'u chung mi dmigs pa las kam las thabs shes rab nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5961: de'i de steng du +aa li k+aa li'i 'khor lo bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5964: zhes brjod pas +aa li k+aa li'i sgras de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs dam bskul bar bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5965: khyad par gyi p+au dza dngos ni /
NK007(ja)001:5966: dang po bdud rtsi brlabs te /
NK007(ja)001:5967: a b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas bdud rtsi'i snod +aahls b+han+d+hara gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5968: b+h+r+aum las 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa bsam /
NK007(ja)001:5969: de'i steng du bdud rtsi dngos gzhi lnga las /
NK007(ja)001:5982: gong bzhin spro bsdu byas nas rigs lnga bdud rtsir zhu /
NK007(ja)001:5983: +amo +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes byin gyis brlab /
NK007(ja)001:5984: badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aah zhes mtheb srin gyis bdud rtsi dkrug cing /
NK007(ja)001:5985: snang srid thams cad ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlab /
NK007(ja)001:5986: +amo badz+ra bi sho d+ha a mri te h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5988: p+au dza bsang zhing nye reg 'thor 'thung bya /
NK007(ja)001:5989: +amo yak+sha kro d+ha a mri te h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:5990: ces khro chung du gyur par bsam te bgegs bskrad do //
NK007(ja)001:5991: de nas gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa ni gsum ste /
NK007(ja)001:5992: dang po sgrub pa'i gtor ma byin gyis brlab te /
NK007(ja)001:5993: b+h+r+aum pad+ma ba lim ta bi shwa tsakra b+h+r+aum /
NK007(ja)001:5994: zhes brjod pas gtor snod b+h+r+aum las zla gam dbang gi gzhal yas khang du gyur /
NK007(ja)001:5995: h'u ha he phata b+h+yo ram zhes brjod pas /
NK007(ja)001:5996: h'u las khrag 'thung rigs lnga yab yum du gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6000: b+h+yo las dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad du bskyed do //
NK007(ja)001:6001: skabs 'dir khrag 'thung gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa mi 'gal lam zhe na /
NK007(ja)001:6002: zhi khro dang phyi nang gsang ba'i tshul du bstan pa yin te mi 'gal lo //
NK007(ja)001:6003: de ni mchod stob kyi gnas so //
NK007(ja)001:6004: gnyis pa mchod pa'i gtor ma ni b+h+r+aum ka p+aa la ba lim ta /
NK007(ja)001:6006: gtor snod b+h+r+aum las b+han+d+ha'i snod yangs shing rgya che ba'i nang /
NK007(ja)001:6007: gtor ma'i rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lngar bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6009: zhes pas de'i steng du ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la h'u bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6012: a tsan+d+ra man+da la +amo zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6013: a las zla ba'i steng du +amo bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6014: s+pha ra na phata kyis 'phags pa mchod /
NK007(ja)001:6016: sam ha ra na h'u gis skye 'gro'i rtsi bcud dang /
NK007(ja)001:6017: ye shes kya bdud rtsi bsdus h'u 'od du zhu nas dngos po'i ma dag pa sbyangs /
NK007(ja)001:6018: +aah'oda du zhu nas bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po lta bur gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6019: +amo 'od du zhu nas 'dod yon gyi lha mo lngar gyur par bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6021: dug gsum sha khrag rus pa'i phung por bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6022: +amo ba lim ta te dz+wa ba lim ta ba
NK007(ja)001:6023: la ba ti gu h+ya tri shwa sa ma ya
NK007(ja)001:6024: s+t+wam / zhes brjod cing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6025: de nas rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6030: b+han+d+ha'i nang du pad+ma dmar po 'dab brgyad lte bar ra dmar pos mtshan par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6032: sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus /
NK007(ja)001:6033: 'od du zhu khrag gi rgya mtshor gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6034: gzar bu rdo rjer gyur pas dkrugs pas rba rlabs
NK007(ja)001:6035: kyi zer ma las 'dod yon gyi lha mor 'phro
NK007(ja)001:6037: +amo rak+ta dz+wa la sa mu tra man+da h'u /
NK007(ja)001:6038: zhes brjod cing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6039: de nas mar me byin gyis brlabs te /
NK007(ja)001:6040: kong bu ltar snang ba ni yum gyi mkha' /
NK007(ja)001:6041: sdong bu ltar snang ba ni yab kyi gsang ba /
NK007(ja)001:6042: mar khu ltar snang ba ni bde ba chen po byang chub kyi sems /
NK007(ja)001:6043: mar me'i 'od ltar snang ba ni don ye shes lnga yi ngo bor bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6044: +amo dz+ny+aa na +aa lo ke sa ma ya h'u /
NK007(ja)001:6045: zhes brjod cing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6046: de nas mchod pa'i bye brag rnams dkyil 'khor du dgod cing 'bul ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6048: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod de dkyil 'khor du dgod cing dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6049: de yan chad kyis sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa bsgom pa'i thabs rdzogs so //
NK007(ja)001:6051: // dngos gzhi gzhung nyams su blang ba bsgom pa'i rim pa ni gnyis te /
NK007(ja)001:6052: rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6053: 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs bsags pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6058: rjes su yi rang ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6059: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6060: mya ngan mi 'da' bar gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6061: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6063: dbang dang byin rlabs zhu ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6065: badz+ra sa ma ya h'u dzah zhes brjod cing se gol brdabs pas /
NK007(ja)001:6066: bla ma dang yi dam gyi lha sangs rgyas dang
NK007(ja)001:6067: byang chub sems dpa' mkha' 'gro chos skyong dang bcas
NK007(ja)001:6068: pa mdun gyi nam mkhar spyan drangs te bzhugs par
NK007(ja)001:6069: bsam / de rnams kyi mdun du bdag gi lus zhing gi rdul snyed dang bcas par sprul te /
NK007(ja)001:6070: zhabs la spyi gtugs kyis lus ngag yid gsum gus pas phyag 'tshal te /
NK007(ja)001:6071: 'jam dpal rdo rje zhes pa'i tshig rkang bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6072: gnyis pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6074: yid kyis sprul pa'i phyi nang gi mchod pa dpag tu med pa blos blangs la 'bul /
NK007(ja)001:6075: sangs rgyas zhing du gang basngagasa zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6076: gsum pa sdig pa bshags pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6077: tshe rabs nas bsags pa'i mi dge ba'i las nyes byas la 'gyod pas bshags /
NK007(ja)001:6078: bdag gis sngon chad ces pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6079: bzhi pa rjes su yi rang bar dbul ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6080: so so'i skye bo dang nyan thos rang sangs rgyas
NK007(ja)001:6081: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' la sogs pa'i dge
NK007(ja)001:6082: ba thams cad la rjes su yi rang ba dbul
NK007(ja)001:6083: / mgon po kun gyi zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6084: lnga pa chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar bskul ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6085: sangs rgyas rnams la sems can gyi don du /
NK007(ja)001:6086: theg pa chen po'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor du gsol ces gsol ba gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6087: bde gshegs byang chub ces pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6088: drug pa mya ngan las mi 'da' bar gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6089: sangs rgyas rnams sems can gyi don la skyo ba skyes nas /
NK007(ja)001:6090: rang don du mya ngan las 'da' bar bzhed pa rnams /
NK007(ja)001:6091: ji srid 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du bzhugs par gsol ba gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6092: mya ngan 'da' bzhed ces pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6093: bdun pa dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6094: de dag las byung ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba thams
NK007(ja)001:6095: cad sems can gyi don du sangs rgyas thob par
NK007(ja)001:6096: bsngo / ji srid 'khor ba zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6098: sems can thams cad kyi don du de bzhin gshegs
NK007(ja)001:6099: ba la bdag gi lus longs sbyod du yang dbul
NK007(ja)001:6101: zhabs tog tu yang dbul la /
NK007(ja)001:6102: bdag kyang dus 'di zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod /
NK007(ja)001:6103: dgu pa byin rlabs zhu ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6104: dbang bzhi'i tshul gyis rim pas dbang bskur bas lung ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa dag nas /
NK007(ja)001:6105: mthar 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas /
NK007(ja)001:6106: rang yang 'od du zhu nas mi dmigs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6107: dus 'di nas ni zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6108: gnyis pa 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs bsags pa ni drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:6109: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6110: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drang zhing bstim pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6113: thun mtshams kyi spyod lam bstan pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6114: mtshams sbyor ba tshogs kyi p+au dza dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6116: sa ma ti gsum bsgom pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6117: 'og gzhi 'byung ba rim brtsegs bskyed pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6118: steng dag pa gzhal yas khang gdan dang bcas pa bskyed pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6119: lha bskyed pa dngos bstan pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6120: dang po ting 'dzin gsum bsgom pa ni gsum las /
NK007(ja)001:6121: dang po de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6122: chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid kun gzhi rang
NK007(ja)001:6123: bzhin gyi stong pa ma bcos pa'i ngang la bzhag
NK007(ja)001:6125: rtog med ces pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6126: gnyis pa kun tu snang ba'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK007(ja)001:6127: de'i ngang las de ltar ma rtog pa'i sems can
NK007(ja)001:6128: thams cad la khyab pa'i snying rje nam mkha' lta
NK007(ja)001:6129: bu stong zhing go phyes pas sems can gyi don
NK007(ja)001:6130: byed par bsgom / chu zla'i zhes pa tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6131: gsum pa rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ni /
NK007(ja)001:6132: snang ba dang stong pa dbyer med pa'i rang bzhin
NK007(ja)001:6133: rig pa nyid yi ge h'u dmar po snang la
NK007(ja)001:6135: s+pha ra na phata kyis 'phags pa mchod /
NK007(ja)001:6137: sam ha ra na h'u gis slar 'dus te /
NK007(ja)001:6138: sngar bas gzi brjid dang ldan par bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6140: yod de yod pa zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6141: de nas gnyis pa 'byung ba rim brtsegs kyi bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6147: ram rnams rim gyis chad pa las /
NK007(ja)001:6148: e mthing nag 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu nas yum kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin /
NK007(ja)001:6149: nam mkha' mthing nag gru gsum rgya khyon dpag tu med pa gcig bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6151: e gru gsum zhes pas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6152: yam ljang gu las 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu //
NK007(ja)001:6153: dam tshig sgrol ma'i rang bzhin rlung gi dkyil 'khor
NK007(ja)001:6154: ljang nag rdo rje rgya gram gyi dbyibs su gyur
NK007(ja)001:6155: / rgya khyon dpag tu med par gyur par bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6156: 'thor byed rlung nag ces pas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6157: ra dmar po las 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu //
NK007(ja)001:6158: m+aa ma k+ai'i rang bzhin khrag gi rgya mtsho dmar
NK007(ja)001:6159: zhing zlum pa rgya khyon dpag tu med pa bsgom
NK007(ja)001:6160: / rak+ta khrag gi zhes pas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6161: sum smug po las 'phro 'dus 'od du zhu nas /
NK007(ja)001:6162: sangs rgyas spyan ma'i rang bzhin zhing gis gzhi dbyibs
NK007(ja)001:6163: gru bzhi pa kha dog dpag tu med pa bsgom
NK007(ja)001:6164: / zhing chen gtams pa'i zhes pas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6166: keng rus kyi ri rab rgya khyon dpag tu med pa bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6167: keng rus chen po'i zhes pa gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6168: ram dmar po 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu nas /
NK007(ja)001:6169: na bza' dkar mo'i rang bzhin /
NK007(ja)001:6170: me'i dkyil 'khor dbyibs gru gsum pa kha dog dmar po rgya khyon dpag tu med par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6171: ye shes 'bar ba'i zhes pas gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6173: gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6174: gdan bskyed pa ste gnyis las /
NK007(ja)001:6176: h'u de las b+h+r+aum smug po chad 'phros 'dus nas 'od du zhu nas /
NK007(ja)001:6178: gzhal yas khang thod pa skam rlon las grub pa'i dbyibs gru bzhi pa /
NK007(ja)001:6179: rak+tasa spyin thabs su sbyar ba /
NK007(ja)001:6180: gnam lcags kyi gzer btab pa /
NK007(ja)001:6181: b+han+d+ha lcang los kha pad byas pa ba su ta dang sbrul nag gi zar tshags byas pas /
NK007(ja)001:6182: chu srin gyi thod pas mda' yab byas pa sgo bzhi yang rus sbal gyi ma them /
NK007(ja)001:6186: phyi dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad /
NK007(ja)001:6187: rdo rje me ris mdzes pa /
NK007(ja)001:6189: dbus gru gsum zla gam dmar po gsum gyis bskor ba /
NK007(ja)001:6190: thod pa skam po'i mu khyud /
NK007(ja)001:6192: gu ru pad+ma phyogs tshon du bzhed /
NK007(ja)001:6193: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ser por bzhed /
NK007(ja)001:6194: d+ha na da la dmar po kho nar bzhed do //
NK007(ja)001:6196: rdo rje'i ra ba mthing ga /
NK007(ja)001:6198: khyams khrag gi rgya mtshor bzhed /
NK007(ja)001:6199: nang gi ka ba yang rus sbal gyi gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6208: gra bzhir zhing gi rgyal mtshan bzhi 'phyar ba bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6209: dur khrod 'bar ba'i zhes tshig brgyad kyis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6210: gnyis pa gdan bskyed pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6211: dbus kyi gru gsum la rak+ta'i rgya mtshor gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6212: ya ma ye ti ra bam /
NK007(ja)001:6213: zhes pas gshin rje pho mo byi chings su bsnol pa'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6215: zhes pas ma he glang rgod pho mo bardzisa pa'i khri /
NK007(ja)001:6218: zhes pas pam las pad+ma'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6220: zhes pas ma las nyi ma'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6222: zhes pas a las zla ba'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6223: dbus kyi gru gsum zhes pa'i tshig lngas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6225: shar gyi rtsibs la dri za pho mo'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6228: byang du gnod sbyin pho mo'i gdan /
NK007(ja)001:6229: rtsibs mchan bzhi la ni mtsho bzhi bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6234: bzhi pa lha bskyed pa la gnyis las /
NK007(ja)001:6236: yan lag gi lha bskyed ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6242: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin de gdan thog tu babs pas /
NK007(ja)001:6246: slar 'dus te 'od du zhu ba las /
NK007(ja)001:6248: zhes pas ye shes kyi tsakra rtsibs brgyad du gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6249: de yang 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu ba las /
NK007(ja)001:6250: +amo sh+r+ai ya m+aan+ta ka ma ru rtse be ta li h'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:6252: skad cig gis gshin rje'i gshed dmar po /
NK007(ja)001:6253: zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog dmar po pad+ma r+aa ga'i mdog 'dra ba /
NK007(ja)001:6254: phyag g.yas pa me'i 'khor lo 'od dang bcas pa /
NK007(ja)001:6255: g.yon pa rlung gi tsakra bsnams pa /
NK007(ja)001:6256: spyan g.yas pa la me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:6257: spyan g.yon pa la las kyi tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:6258: shangs nas bskal ba'i rlung nag 'tshub pa /
NK007(ja)001:6259: ag tshom dmar ser las bskal pa'i me stag 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:6260: mche ba g.yas pa las rak+ta'i chu chen shing rta'i 'phang lo tsam 'bab pa /
NK007(ja)001:6261: mche ba g.yon pa las ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK007(ja)001:6262: lcags kyu lta bu 'phros pas dgra bgegs kyi tsit+ta
NK007(ja)001:6263: 'dren pa / dbu skra kham nag 'khyil ba'i skra gseb nas /
NK007(ja)001:6264: sprul pa'i khro chung mang po 'phro ba /
NK007(ja)001:6265: ral pa'i rtse la b+han+d+ha lcang los brgyan pa /
NK007(ja)001:6266: sku stod la zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi /
NK007(ja)001:6267: klang chen gyi ko rlon gsol ba /
NK007(ja)001:6268: sku smad la stag gi sham thabs gsol ba /
NK007(ja)001:6269: thod pa skam po lnga'i dbu rgyan byas pa /
NK007(ja)001:6270: thod rlon lnga bcu rtsa bzhi'i do shal /
NK007(ja)001:6271: sbrul rigs lngas snyan cha dang /
NK007(ja)001:6277: zhabs gnyis brkyang bskum gyi tshul du bzhugs pa /
NK007(ja)001:6278: zhal nas h'u phata kyi sgra sgrog pa /
NK007(ja)001:6279: de lta bu gcig bdag nyid sal ler bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6280: 'jam dpal khros pa zhes pa'i tshig lngas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6281: gnyis pa yum bskyed pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6282: thugs ka nas yi ge trag gcig g.yon du chad pa las 'phros 'dus 'od du zhu nas /
NK007(ja)001:6283: trag rak+sha ma ma e ka dz+aa ti dzahdzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6284: yum chen e ka dz+aa ti sku mdog dmar smug rgya skyegs kyi kha dog 'dra ba /
NK007(ja)001:6285: zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas tri shu la thogs nas yab la 'khyud pa /
NK007(ja)001:6286: g.yon pas thod khrag gtso la stob pa /
NK007(ja)001:6287: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan pa /
NK007(ja)001:6288: shin tu khro zhing rngams pa la /
NK007(ja)001:6289: cung zad 'dzum pa'i mdangs kyis yab la blta zhing /
NK007(ja)001:6290: sbyor ba'i p+au dza dbul bar bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6291: de dang gnyis su med zhes pa'i tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6292: gsum pa 'khor bskyed pa ni gsum ste /
NK007(ja)001:6297: bsnyen sgrub kyi dus su mkha' gsang nas bskyed par yang bshad /
NK007(ja)001:6298: yang bsnyen sgrub las sbyor gyi dus gnyis ka la gnas bzhi nas bskyed pa yang bshad do //
NK007(ja)001:6299: mkha' gsang nas bskyed pa gzhan dang 'dra /
NK007(ja)001:6300: gnas bzhi nas bskyed pa ni gtso bo'i spyan las
NK007(ja)001:6301: dzahdamara po gcig shar phyogs kyi rtsi bas kyi steng
NK007(ja)001:6303: pra ma r+aa dza ni dzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6304: shar du srin po ma ru rtse bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6305: de yang bsnyen sgrub kyi skabs su na bza' dang
NK007(ja)001:6306: chibs med par khro bo kho na bsgom par bshad
NK007(ja)001:6307: la / sku mdog yang gu ru pad+ma'i bzhed kyis so sor bzhed la /
NK007(ja)001:6308: d+ha na da la'i bzhed kyis dmar po kho nar bzhed do //
NK007(ja)001:6310: gtso bo dang mthun pa dur khrod kyis rgyan gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6315: gtso bo'i shangs nas dzahdamara po gcig lho phyogs kyi rtsi bas la 'thon /
NK007(ja)001:6317: ya ma r+aa dza ni dzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6318: gshin rje ma ru rtse g.yas be con /
NK007(ja)001:6320: yum yang g.yas pa yab la 'khyud pa g.yon thod pa 'dzin pa /
NK007(ja)001:6322: yang gtso bo'i ljags las dzahdamara po gcig nub phyogs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs la 'thon /
NK007(ja)001:6324: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba dzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6325: nub tu bdud ma ru rtse g.yas g.yon ral gri zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK007(ja)001:6327: yang thugs ka nas dzahdamara po gcig byang phyogs kyi 'khor lo'i rtsibs la 'thon /
NK007(ja)001:6329: ku be r+aa dza dzah zhes pas /
NK007(ja)001:6330: byang du gnod sbyin ma ru rtse /
NK007(ja)001:6331: g.yas ldan mkhar g.yon thod pa 'dzin pa /
NK007(ja)001:6333: smad las las sbyor gyis dus su rang rang gi bskul dang mthun par bsgom par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6334: gnyis med 'khril zhes pa tshig drug gis gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6335: gnyis pa bswe mo bskyed pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6336: gtso bo'i yan lag bzhi las ma bzhi rtsibs mchan la 'thon /
NK007(ja)001:6340: yo gi shwa ri ya ma tsit+ta /
NK007(ja)001:6341: zhes brjod pas bstod bsnyen sgrub kyi skabs su khro
NK007(ja)001:6342: mo'i cha lugs dur khrod kyi chas kyis brgyan pa
NK007(ja)001:6343: / sku mdog yang bzhed lugs gong dang 'dra /
NK007(ja)001:6344: phyag mtshan ni g.yas pa rigs bzhi'i rang brtags kyi phyag rgya 'dzin pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6345: smad las kyi dus su rang rang gi bskul dang mthun par bskyed do //
NK007(ja)001:6346: 'jam dpal yan lag ces tshig bzhis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6347: gsum pa 'khor gzhan bskyed pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6348: khyams la ging pho mo dgu dgu ste bco brgyad bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6349: de yang bsnyen sgrub kyi dus su /
NK007(ja)001:6350: ye shes kyi ging khro bo dang khro mo'i cha lugs can rang bzhin gyis yod pa tsam bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6351: sgo bzhir bswe yi skyes bu bzhi /
NK007(ja)001:6352: bsnyen sgrub kyi dus su khro bo'i cha lugs su bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6359: smad las kyi dus su bswe yi gyi ling dang /
NK007(ja)001:6360: bya khra la sogs pa chibs pa ste /
NK007(ja)001:6361: bskul dang yang mthun par bskyed do //
NK007(ja)001:6363: de yang bsnyen sgrub kyi dus su ni /
NK007(ja)001:6364: rtsa ba'i lha kho nas chog yang gsung ngo //
NK007(ja)001:6365: gnyis pa yan lag gi lha bskyed pa la gnyis te /
NK007(ja)001:6366: ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6367: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6370: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs dam bskul /
NK007(ja)001:6371: sangs rgyas thams cad rigs lnga'i ngo bor bsdus mchod pa phul /
NK007(ja)001:6374: 'od du zhu nas dbu'i gnas lngar thim /
NK007(ja)001:6376: phung po lnga rigs lngar sangs rgyas /
NK007(ja)001:6377: dbang rtags su dbu'i thod pa'i khang bu lngar yab
NK007(ja)001:6378: la khro bo rigs lnga yum la khro mo rigs
NK007(ja)001:6379: lnga 'khor rnams la rigs so so'i dbu rgyan gyis
NK007(ja)001:6380: mtshan par bsgom / h'u badz+ra ku la zhes pas gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6382: spyi bo dung khang gi nang du a las zla
NK007(ja)001:6383: ba la 'khor lo dkar po +amo gyis mtshan pa
NK007(ja)001:6384: / mgrin par pam las pad+ma dmar po +aamhgisa mtshan pa /
NK007(ja)001:6385: thugs dkar ma las nyi ma'i steng du rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6387: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bor bsdus /
NK007(ja)001:6388: 'od du zhu nas gnas gsum du thim pas sku gsung thugs kyi lhar gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6389: de yang rnam snang gi dung khang 'khor lo +amo gyi mtshan pa /
NK007(ja)001:6390: mtha' yas kyi mgrin par pad+ma +aamh gis mtshan pa /
NK007(ja)001:6391: mi bskyod pa'i thugs kar rdo rje h'u gis mtshan pa bskyed do //
NK007(ja)001:6392: de ya nga bsnyen pa'i dus su zhi ba la sgrub pa /
NK007(ja)001:6393: man chad khro bo ru bshad do //
NK007(ja)001:6394: +amo a kro te ka zhes pas gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6395: spyi don gnyis pa ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs pa la bzhi ste /
NK007(ja)001:6398: gnyis su med par bstims pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6399: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6401: thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas 'og min
NK007(ja)001:6402: chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang rang bzhin lhun gyis
NK007(ja)001:6403: grub pa nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dgongs pa
NK007(ja)001:6404: chos nyid kyi ngang la bzhugs pa de longs spyod
NK007(ja)001:6405: rdzogs pa'i skur rong gis bzhengs te /
NK007(ja)001:6406: 'gro ba'i don la byon ma rag par bsgom /
NK007(ja)001:6407: dad pa dang ni zhes pa tshig bcu gnyis kyis gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6408: gnyis pa spyan drangs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6409: thugs ka nas dzahmh'u bam hohbazhi las /
NK007(ja)001:6410: dzahls lha mo lcags kyu ma /
NK007(ja)001:6413: hohls dril bu mar gyur te /
NK007(ja)001:6414: yes shes kyi dkyil 'khor rnams lcags kyu mas thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK007(ja)001:6415: zhags pa mas gnas nas spyan drangs /
NK007(ja)001:6416: lcags sgrog mas gnas nas bskyod /
NK007(ja)001:6417: dril bu mas dgyes pa bskyed cing mdun gyi nam
NK007(ja)001:6418: mkha' la me dpung 'dab 'dres kyis tshul du yer
NK007(ja)001:6421: dmar nag gru gsum zhes pa'i tshig bco lngas gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6422: yab gcig sku mchog ces pa'i tshig bcus yum spyan drangs zhing gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6423: 'jam dpal sku mchog ces pa'i tshig bdun gyis dmag dpon spyan drangs zhing gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6425: bswe mo bzhi spyan drangs zhing gsal gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6426: gsum pa gnyis su med par bstim pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6428: ces pas gzhal yas khang dang thugs kyi sgo dbye /
NK007(ja)001:6430: zhes pas chu dang 'o ma 'dres pa ltar /
NK007(ja)001:6431: dam tshig pa dang ye shes pa dbyer med du bstim par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6432: bzhi pa brtan par bzhugs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6433: bdag gi bsam pa ma grub kyi bar ram /
NK007(ja)001:6434: sems can gyi don ma rdzogs kyi bar du gzhan du mi gshegs par bzhugs par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6435: mgon po thugs rje zhes pa tshig bcu bdun gyi rim par gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6436: spyi don gsum pa mchod pa 'bul ba ni drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:6437: gnyis su med par phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6438: thun mong gi p+au dza dbul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6439: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6440: 'dod yon gtor ma'i mchod pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6441: dam rdzas rak+ta'i mchod pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6442: dug lnga rnam dag gi mchod pa'o //
NK007(ja)001:6444: la la dam tshig pa mdun 'thon te /
NK007(ja)001:6445: ye shes pa la phyag dang p+au dza dbul bar 'dod pa yang yod /
NK007(ja)001:6446: 'dir ye shes pa dang dam tshig pa dbyer med
NK007(ja)001:6447: par mjal bas rtogs pa don gyi phyag ces bya
NK007(ja)001:6448: ste / dbyer med pa don gyis 'tshal ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6450: gdug pa 'dul mdzad ces pa'i tshig lngas gtso bo la 'tshal /
NK007(ja)001:6451: 'og ma 'og ma rnams la tshig gsum gsum gyis 'tshal lo //
NK007(ja)001:6452: gnyis pa thun mong gi p+au dza ni /
NK007(ja)001:6453: phyi ltar du 'jig rten gyi khams na yod pa'i yon chab dang /
NK007(ja)001:6459: rol mo la sogs pa lha mo rnams kyi phyag na bsnams nas dbul bar bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6460: nang ltar du bam chen mo las byung ba'i rak+ta'i ar+g+ham dang /
NK007(ja)001:6462: dbang po lnga'i me tog dang /
NK007(ja)001:6467: rkang gling gi dung la sogs pa dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6468: gsang ba ni byang chub sems kyi p+au dza dbul ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6469: tshig ni rtsa ba'i sngags dang /
NK007(ja)001:6470: e dam ar+g+ham d+d+h+aup+pe la sogs pas dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6471: gsum pa bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa la bzhi ste /
NK007(ja)001:6472: sman gyi che ba'i yon tan brjod de spyir 'bul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6473: bye brag tu dbul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6474: bshags pa bya zhing dngos grub blang ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6475: gsang mnan gyi sbreng mchod dbul ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6477: rang byung gdod nas zhes pa'i tshig lngas gsal gdab cing byin gyis brlab /
NK007(ja)001:6478: rgyal ba rgya mtsho zhes tshig bzhis spyir dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6480: mtheb srin nyi zla'i ga'u kha sbyor gyis bdud rtsi bcus te /
NK007(ja)001:6481: lha so so'i zhal du sib sib song bar bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6482: de nas bye brag lha so so la dbul ba la drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:6483: dang po bla ma brgyud pa dang bcas pa la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6484: de nas zhi ba la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6485: de nas khro bo la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6486: de nas bskal ba me ltar gyis ya m+aan+ta ka la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6487: dpal chen sku la gnyis med kyis yum la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6488: de nas dmar po yab yum dang gtso bo /
NK007(ja)001:6492: bswe yi skyes bu la sogs pa la gzhung bzhin dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6496: mchod mgron ci rigs pa la dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6498: rang rig ye shes kyis bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6500: gong gi lha rnams kyi sku gsung thugs nas /
NK007(ja)001:6501: sid+d+hi'i rang bzhin +amo +aahmh'u gsum bdud rtsi'i nang du byung nas /
NK007(ja)001:6502: dpal ldan rdo rje zhes pa'i tshig bzhi brjod cing /
NK007(ja)001:6503: mtheb srin gyis blangs la lce thog tu bzhag /
NK007(ja)001:6504: k+aa ya sid+d+hi la sogs pa brjod pas /
NK007(ja)001:6507: snying ga'i gnas su thim pas /
NK007(ja)001:6508: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob par bsam mo //
NK007(ja)001:6511: dug lnga bdud rtsi zhes pa'i tshig dang /
NK007(ja)001:6512: sngags kyi gtor mar sbreng zhing dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6513: bzhi pa gtor ma'i p+au dza ni /
NK007(ja)001:6514: mchod pa'i gtor ma 'dod yon gyi lha mo lngar bsam la /
NK007(ja)001:6515: dkyil 'khor lha yi dbang po lnga la thim par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6517: dme gtor zhes pa'i tshig drug dang sngags kyi dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6518: lnga pa dam rdzas rak+ta'i p+au dza ni /
NK007(ja)001:6519: phyi ltar du rak+ta 'dod yon gyi lha mor bsam la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6520: nang ltar du dgra bgegs kyi sha khrag tu bsam la dbul /
NK007(ja)001:6521: yab gcig 'jam dpal zhes pa'i tshig gi go rim
NK007(ja)001:6522: bzhin du rang rang gi dam rdzas dang rak+ta dbul
NK007(ja)001:6523: lo // drug pa dug lnga rnam dag gi p+au dza ni /
NK007(ja)001:6524: rdzas rak+ta'i dngos pa gcig la dgra bgegs kyi dngos po bstim te /
NK007(ja)001:6525: gti mug sha dang 'dod chags khrag /
NK007(ja)001:6528: phrag dog don snying rnams dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams
NK007(ja)001:6529: la phul bas bsgral bya'i nyon mongs pa lnga dag
NK007(ja)001:6530: nas / bdag gis sku gsung thugs dang yon tan
NK007(ja)001:6531: phrin las rnam pa lnga'i dngos grub thob par bsam
NK007(ja)001:6532: nas / / de ka la yul sems gnyis ka la sbyor ba'i p+au dza dang /
NK007(ja)001:6533: khams gsum yongs su sgrol ba'i p+au dza rdzogs so //
NK007(ja)001:6534: mgon po gshin rje zhes tshig sum cu so drug sngags dang bcas pas dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6535: spyi don bzhi pa bzlas pa bya ba'i rim pa ni lnga ste /
NK007(ja)001:6542: b+han+d+ha dum bu bzhi pa'i nang du yungs kar rgyal po la phur pa bkod de /
NK007(ja)001:6543: lhar gsal ba'i sgo nas 'phro 'du bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6544: de yang gu ru pad+ma'i bzhed kyi phata dzah zhes
NK007(ja)001:6545: pas mdun du ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor phye ba
NK007(ja)001:6547: d+ha na da la'i bzhed kyis /
NK007(ja)001:6548: ye shes pa dang dam tshig mi dbye bar snod
NK007(ja)001:6549: bcud lha'i dkyil 'khor du gsal ba la spro bsdu
NK007(ja)001:6550: bya'o // de yang bdag gi tsit+ta rat+na gur phub pa 'dra ba'i nang na /
NK007(ja)001:6551: rak+ta zur brgyad lta bu'i lte ba la /
NK007(ja)001:6552: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang ba /
NK007(ja)001:6553: de'i thugs kar ye shes kyi 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad /
NK007(ja)001:6554: de'i lte ba la rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK007(ja)001:6555: de'i lte ba la h'u dmar po yungs 'bru tsam /
NK007(ja)001:6556: tsakra rtsibs brgyad la sngags kyi phreng ba me stag lta bus bskor ba de las 'od zer byung /
NK007(ja)001:6557: ljags steng dang dung khang brgyud de /
NK007(ja)001:6559: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang /
NK007(ja)001:6560: nang bcud kyi sems can lha /
NK007(ja)001:6561: dbyings gting mtha' med pa nas /
NK007(ja)001:6562: skye 'gro gzugs kyis bsdus pa thams cad lhar gsal ba ni sku'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK007(ja)001:6563: yang gong bzhin ljags steng nas 'phros pas sgra thams
NK007(ja)001:6564: cad sngags kyi sgrar gyur pa ni gsung gi dkyil
NK007(ja)001:6565: 'khor ro // yang thugs ka nas 'phros te sku snang stong dbyer med /
NK007(ja)001:6567: thugs gsal stong dbyer med du gsal ba ni thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK007(ja)001:6568: de yang 'od zer phar 'phros pas mchod pa phul thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK007(ja)001:6569: tshur bsdus te sid+d+hi thob par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6570: de yang las dang po pas rim pas bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6571: gu ru pad+ma'i bzhed pa dang mthun /
NK007(ja)001:6572: dus gcig tu bsgom pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6573: d+ha na da la dang mthun no //
NK007(ja)001:6576: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ku m+aa ra ya ma r+aa dzahmh'u phata /
NK007(ja)001:6578: bzlas pa'i grangs ni bdun 'bum dang nyi khri'o //
NK007(ja)001:6579: bzlas pa'i tshad ni rab dngos /
NK007(ja)001:6581: tha ma rmi ltas kyi rtags ma byung gi bar du'o //
NK007(ja)001:6582: lnga pa thun mtshams kyi spyod pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6583: bsgom pa'i skyon bying ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6585: 'thor ba la sogs pa'i skyon bcos te /
NK007(ja)001:6586: h'u gi chos lngar shes par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6587: bsgom pa la skyo na bzlas pa la brtson par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6589: bdag cag dam tshig 'di la zhes pas lhag chad bshags te /
NK007(ja)001:6590: de nas dgung la thog thog gis ya m+aan+ta ka yab yum la bstod /
NK007(ja)001:6591: dpal 'bar dbang phyug gis gtso bo la bstod /
NK007(ja)001:6592: 'jam dpal thugs las zhes 'khor la bstod /
NK007(ja)001:6593: de nas se gol dkrol zhing 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6594: smon lam gdab par bya ste /
NK007(ja)001:6596: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NK007(ja)001:6597: cad dang bcom ldan 'das gshin rje'i gshed kyi lha
NK007(ja)001:6598: tshogs rnams mkhyen par mdzad cing bdag la dgongs su
NK007(ja)001:6599: gsol / bdag gis rgyal ba'i bka' bden pa 'di 'grub par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:6600: mchog thun mong gi dngos grub thob par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:6601: bdag gis sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa bsrung bar gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:6602: mthar bla na med pa'i sangs rgyas thob par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:6603: thob nas sems can gyi don byed par gyur cig /
NK007(ja)001:6604: ces lan gsum gsum brjod do //
NK007(ja)001:6605: skabs su tshogs kyi p+au dza yang bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6607: rtag pa'i mtha' bsal ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor bsdu'o //
NK007(ja)001:6608: chad pa'i mtha' bsal phyir lha rdzogs tshul du bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6610: 'gro nyal 'dug sdod za 'chag spyod lam ci byed
NK007(ja)001:6611: kyang lha yi nga rgyal las ma yengs par bya'o
NK007(ja)001:6612: // nye bar bsnyen pa'i dus su /
NK007(ja)001:6613: dngos grub rtags kyi bsnyen pa zhes kyang bya /
NK007(ja)001:6614: ye shes kyi lha nye bar bsnyen pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK007(ja)001:6615: gong bzhin sku gsung thugs kyi gnas nas 'od zer 'phros te /
NK007(ja)001:6616: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs dam bskul /
NK007(ja)001:6617: rig 'dzin pho mo gzi mdangs bskyed /
NK007(ja)001:6618: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du bsdus /
NK007(ja)001:6619: dregs pa can thams cad bran du bkol /
NK007(ja)001:6620: slar 'dus pas sngar bas gzi brjid dang ldan pa sgom la nye bar bsnyen pa'i sngags ni /
NK007(ja)001:6621: +amo sh+r+ai many+dzu ya ma r+aa dza ma ma e ka dz+aa ti dza dzah zhes bzlas so //
NK007(ja)001:6622: bzlas pa'i grangs ni 'bum phrag gcig go //
NK007(ja)001:6624: drod bdun pa ltar shes so //
NK007(ja)001:6625: mthun mtshams kyi spyod pa ni gong dang mthun no //
NK007(ja)001:6626: de ltar nye bar bsnyen pa rdzogs nas sgrub pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6627: sgrub pa chen po ni sgrub pa'i bkol byang nang nas 'byung ba bzhin du bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6628: las la sbyar ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6629: las sbyor gyi skabs shes par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6630: drug pa mtshams sbyor ba tshogs kyi p+au dza ni drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:6632: bsang zhing byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6633: tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal gdab cing byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6634: p+au dza spyir dbul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6638: tshogs kyi p+au dza bzab dang /
NK007(ja)001:6641: ldag pa la sogs pa 'dod yon lnga'i bye brag tshang bar bsham mo //
NK007(ja)001:6643: phyi ltar du tram las rat+na'i snod yangs shing rgya
NK007(ja)001:6644: che ba las bcud lha'i zhal zas ro mchog brgya
NK007(ja)001:6646: nang ltar du snod a las b+han+d+ha 'bar bar gyur /
NK007(ja)001:6647: bcud sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i phung por gyur par bsam /
NK007(ja)001:6648: de nas a mri ta'i sngags kyis bdud rtsis bsang gtor byas la /
NK007(ja)001:6649: ram yam kham gis dngos po bsreg pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6652: de nas +amo +aahmh'u gsum bskyed cing ngag tu yang brjod la /
NK007(ja)001:6653: h'u gis dngos po'i skyon sbyangs /
NK007(ja)001:6655: +amo gyis 'dod yon lngar byin gyis brlab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6657: b+h+r+aum zhes pas gzhal yas khang du gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6658: rtsa sngags kyi lha gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6659: de nas rol mo dang bcas pas /
NK007(ja)001:6660: dmar nag drag po'i zhes tshig bzhis spyan drangs zhing gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6663: bla med mchog gi zhes tshig bco lngas bcu drug /
NK007(ja)001:6664: tshogs 'dod yon gyi lha mor bsam la sbyor dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6665: lnga pa thugs dam bskang ba ni /
NK007(ja)001:6666: bskang ngo bskal pa'i zhes pas so so'i mtshan nas brjod de bskang ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6668: phud spros la dang pos mchod de /
NK007(ja)001:6669: bcom ldan 'jam dpal zhes pa'i tshig bzhis dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6671: bcom ldan 'jam dpal zhes tshig bzhis dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6673: dgra bgegs kyi gzugs byas la dgug gzhug bya /
NK007(ja)001:6674: mtshon chas gtub la bstab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6676: khrag 'thung 'jigs byed ces pa tshig drug gis dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6677: de nas rig 'dzin chos skyong dben gnas la sogs pa'i rigs su gyur pa la'ang dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6678: de nas rnam 'byor pa lhar gsal bas tshogs la rol pa tshul bzhin du bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6679: lhag ma gsog 'jog med par bzhag /
NK007(ja)001:6680: tshogs kyi smon lam yang gdab bo //
NK007(ja)001:6681: tha ma cho ga'i mjug bsdu ba ni drug ste /
NK007(ja)001:6682: gtor ma'i sgo nas lhag chog bya ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6683: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6685: gtor gzhong la bro brdung ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6687: rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6691: yar gnas ye shes kyi lha la mchod pa dang /
NK007(ja)001:6692: mar gnas ye shes kyi sprul ba dang /
NK007(ja)001:6695: dpal gyi gtor ma lhar gsal gdab /
NK007(ja)001:6696: gtor ma'i p+au dza gong bzhin du gsal gdab la /
NK007(ja)001:6698: nam mkha' yangs pa'i zhes tshig bzhis spyan drangs /
NK007(ja)001:6699: sh+r+ai many+dzu zhes pa'i sngags kyis dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6700: 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab cing sid+d+hi blangs /
NK007(ja)001:6702: zhes ye shes pa rnams rang la bsdu /
NK007(ja)001:6703: de nas gtor ma shod du phab la bsangs sbyangs byin gyis brlab /
NK007(ja)001:6704: de nas sprul pa'i lha tshogs la mchod de /
NK007(ja)001:6705: bcom ldan 'jam dpal zhes pa'i tshig gsum cu rtsa drug gis gtso bo dang /
NK007(ja)001:6706: dmag dpon dang bswe mo dang bal mo mchod do //
NK007(ja)001:6707: de nas mar gnas 'jig rten pa la sbyin pa ni /
NK007(ja)001:6708: lhag phud rnams mtshams sbyar la /
NK007(ja)001:6710: dur khrod kyi ma mo dang /
NK007(ja)001:6712: bdud dang gshin rje dang rgyal po la sogs pa la sbyin no //
NK007(ja)001:6714: gtor ma byin gyis brlab la /
NK007(ja)001:6715: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan 'di la tshig rkang mang nyung
NK007(ja)001:6716: nyer bdun pa dang nyer gnyis la gnyis du snang
NK007(ja)001:6717: ngo // zhes bcu gnyis kyis dbul lo //
NK007(ja)001:6718: de nas phyir rol du brtan ma bskyang /
NK007(ja)001:6719: nang du log la dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo /
NK007(ja)001:6721: gtor gzhong la phrin las bzhi'i bro brdung /
NK007(ja)001:6723: rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya'o //
NK007(ja)001:6724: bkra shis gsol ba la sogs pa yang bya gsung ngo //
NK007(ja)001:6725: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma'i don du phrin las kyi sgom byang dang /
NK007(ja)001:6726: rgyun du nyams su len pa'i mngon rtogs thun mong du gzhung dang /
NK007(ja)001:6727: bla ma'i gsung ngag dang mi 'gal bar /
NK007(ja)001:6728: gnubs kyi ban+de bkra shis dar gyis sbyar ba'o //
NK007(ja)001:6731: // snod ngan dam tshig med pa'i lag tu shor ra re /
NK007(ja)001:6734: bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gshin rje'i gshed dmar po'i
NK007(ja)001:6735: sgom byang ngag tu brjod tshul dang bcas pa bzhugs
NK007(ja)001:6736: so // 'jam pa'i dbyangs la phyag 'tshal lo //
